{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120172_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "新人矿工",
            "context": "果真是你啊……\\n“赤臂戈尔德”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "我不知道你在说什么。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120172_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "新人矿工",
            "context": "装蒜也没用。\\n我可认得你那只假肢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120172_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "新人矿工",
            "context": "我就是为了找你才来的。\\n你真正该待的地方\\n可不是什么矿山吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "我只是一介矿工，\\n就该在山里挖石头。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120172_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "新人矿工",
            "context": "真是倔啊。你的“赤臂”被你\\n用来挖石头，可要哭了哦？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "你说什么我听不懂。\\n我这手臂不是什么赤臂，是铁臂。\\n虽然不好看，但挖石头很好用。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120172_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "新人矿工",
            "context": "没关系，把它再变成“赤臂”就行了。\\n我知道“赤臂”这名号的来历哦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120172_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "新人矿工",
            "context": "只要再把它染成血红色\\n不就好了嘛，嘻嘻嘻……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120172_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "新人矿工",
            "context": "你应该待在“那个人”身边……\\n你知道的吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "不管你说什么，我都不知道。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120172_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "新人矿工",
            "context": "嘁，你要是执意装蒜的话，\\n就让我看看你那胡须下\\n到底是什么样子。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120172_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "新人矿工",
            "context": "你似乎还特意留了胡须\\n试图掩盖，但不管你怎么掩盖，\\n“证据”都是不会消失的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "住口……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120172_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "新人矿工",
            "context": "想让我住口你就干脆点承认，\\n然后跟我一起回那个人身边。\\n不然的话……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "不然就怎样？你以为\\n你能奈何得了我吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120172_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "新人矿工",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "你说你知道“赤臂”的来历是吧？\\n那要不要亲身体验一下\\n“赤臂”是怎么诞生的？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120172_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "新人矿工",
            "context": "慢、慢着……这样好吗？\\n我背后可有那个人呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "没出息的家伙。\\n如果关键时刻只会借他人威风，\\n一开始就别威胁别人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "滚回去。告诉那家伙，\\n不管过去发生过什么……\\n现在这里才是我的归宿。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120172_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "新人矿工",
            "context": "呃……你要拒绝“那个人”吗。\\n你可别后悔！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "矿工",
            "context": "咦，那个新人呢？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "他在我的指导下叫苦不迭，\\n辞职了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "矿工",
            "context": "诶！？竟然指导得让人辞职……\\n戈尔德老爷子，\\n你又摆臭脸了吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "是啊……真是惭愧。\\n没想到不动点粗，都没法把\\n自己的意思传达给别人……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "结果……\\n我还是和从前一样啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "矿工",
            "context": "戈尔德老爷子？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "啊，抱歉。没什么。\\n作为一介矿工，继续干活了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120169_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "安洁",
            "context": "爷爷，你回来啦！\\n今天的活儿都干完了吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "是啊，安洁。\\n有孙女特意出门迎接，\\n我真是太幸福啦！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120169_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "安洁",
            "context": "哎呀，爷爷你真是的，\\n总那么小题大做……咦？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120169_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "安洁",
            "context": "爷爷，你的胡子脏了。\\n我帮你擦擦！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "住、住手！别碰我！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120169_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "安洁",
            "context": "呀！？啊、啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "啊……抱歉，安洁！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120169_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "安洁",
            "context": "哈啊、哈啊……爷爷……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "安洁……不好，又发作了……\\n抱歉，安洁……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120169_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "安洁",
            "context": "对不起，爷爷……\\n我……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "不，都是爷爷不好。\\n都怪爷爷。你没有错。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "戈尔德",
            "context": "错的，是我才对……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "与此同时——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "是吗，总算找到他了啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120172_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "恶徒手下",
            "context": "是的！不会错的 ，\\n他就是“赤臂戈尔德”！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "那你怎么没把他带回来？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120172_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "恶徒手下",
            "context": "那、那家伙不听我的话，\\n所以我觉得还是先回来\\n跟老大报告一下比较好……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "我的命令是把他带回来！\\n你的想法比我的命令\\n还重要吗？啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120172_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "恶徒手下",
            "context": "这、这……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "拖下去。\\n我不需要不听话的家伙。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01b"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "恶徒手下",
            "context": "怎么这样！我为你\\n拼死拼活地卖命……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120044_01",
                "120172_01",
                "120044_01b"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "恶徒手下",
            "context": "不、不要……放开我……\\n放开我、放开我、放开我！\\n不要啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "“这边”的世界可没有那么单纯，\\n不是拼了命就有回报的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120170_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "你更适合“这边”……\\n“赤臂戈尔德”……呵呵呵……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}